    <h1>Nofollow Link</h1>
    <p class="description">A hyperlink with <code>rel="nofollow"</code> that signals search engines to withhold link equity from the destination. About <strong>43% of all backlinks</strong> on the web are nofollow — and they still matter for SEO.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
      <div class="meta-author">
        <div class="meta-avatar">AVR</div>
        <div class="meta-author-info">
          <span class="meta-author-name"><a href="/authors/akshay-vr/">Akshay VR</a></span>
          <span class="meta-author-role">Marketing Head · theStacc</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-divider"></div>
